  "remarks": "Behnam Sahriyari Trading Company is owned by Behnam Sahriyari, who leads the Islamic Revolutionary Guard Corps (IRGC) Quds Force Unit 190, which conducts arms smuggling operations. He uses his company as a front for IRGC weapons transfers. Therefore, Behnam Sahriyari Trading Company is involved in the shipment of arms on behalf of the IRGC.",
